#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.89"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.89:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.89:0.2"
msgid "9. Sītivagga"
msgstr "9. Coolness"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.89:0.3"
msgid "89. Appahāyasutta"
msgstr "89. Not Giving Up"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.438"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.89:1.1"
msgid "“Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme appahāya abhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, without giving up six things you can’t become accomplished in "
"view."

msgctxt "an6.89:1.2"
msgid "Katame cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.89:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sakkāyadiṭṭhiṃ, vicikicchaṃ, sīlabbataparāmāsaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ rāgaṃ, "
"apāyagamanīyaṃ dosaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ mohaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Identity view, doubt, misapprehension of precepts and observances, and forms "
"of greed, hate, and delusion that lead to rebirth in places of loss."

msgctxt "an6.89:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme appahāya abhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"Without giving up these six things you can’t become accomplished in view."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.89:2.1"
msgid "Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme pahāya bhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātuṃ."
msgstr "After giving up six things you can become accomplished in view."

msgctxt "an6.89:2.2"
msgid "Katame cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.89:2.3"
msgid ""
"Sakkāyadiṭṭhiṃ, vicikicchaṃ, sīlabbataparāmāsaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ rāgaṃ, "
"apāyagamanīyaṃ dosaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ mohaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Identity view, doubt, misapprehension of precepts and observances, and forms "
"of greed, hate, and delusion that lead to rebirth in places of loss."

msgctxt "an6.89:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme pahāya bhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātun”ti."
msgstr "After giving up these six things you can become accomplished in view.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.89:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
